                              <roleName type="dead">witib</roleName> des Pierbaumer</rs>,</rs>
                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__otto_pierbaumer_QGW_II_I_1494">Ott der Pierbaumer,
                        sein <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__andreas_pierbaumer_QGW_II_I_1494">prueder</roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__stephan_seifrid_QGW_II_I_1494">Stephan Seifrid von
